long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Simple Chrome helper for University of Washington course registration.

NO MORE SLN COPY AND PASTE
Works best with Notify.UW
You know what 5 seconds means during registration :)


Features of beta version:

- Address bar quick course navigation: type "hr" + [course abbr] + [course#] will navigate to the corresponding course in time schedule.

- One-click registration: add buttons in time schedule and enrollment summary page.
Click the button will automatically open the registration page and fill out the SLN.

- Select a different quarter by changing the configuration in "options"


Still in development. Let me know your feedback :)

PS: Don't ask me about automatic registration - that violates the regulation of UW :(
